A massive prehistoric mammoth perfectly preserved in a translucent blue ice block, positioned in the center of a modern server room with blinking equipment and cables surrounding it. The mammoth's ancient tusks and fur are visible through the crystalline ice, creating a stark contrast between the prehistoric creature and the contemporary technology environment. Frost crystals spread across nearby server racks, and cold mist drifts along the floor. The lighting is dramatic with cool blue tones from the ice mixing with warm amber indicator lights from the servers. Photorealistic style with sharp detail on the ice textures and the mammoth's preserved features.
